Package: bayeswatch
Title: Bayesian Sampler Viewer for Stan Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("bayeswatch", "author", email = "author@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Opens an animated MCMC visualization in the RStudio Viewer pane
    while brms or rethinking models are sampling. Wraps Chi Feng's MCMC demo.
